document_data.caption: A map showing Kingsbay in southern Gwynneth.
document_data.name: Kingsbay
document_data.mainbody: '''Kingsbay''' was a small coastal town located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Kingsbay was found at the end of [[Corwell Road]] in the kingdom of [[Corwell]] in southeast Gwynneth. The town sat along the coast of the [[Strait of Alaron]] on the [[Kingsbay]] for which it was named.
